table:columns.name: id
table:columns.description: Globally unique identifier for the building feature.

table:columns.name: geometry
table:columns.description: Building footprint geometry as a Well-Known Binary (WKB) Polygon or MultiPolygon.

table:columns.name: bbox
table:columns.description: Bounding box of the building geometry formatted as [xmin, ymin, xmax, ymax].

table:columns.name: type
table:columns.description: Feature type; typically 'building' for all entries in this theme.

table:columns.name: sources
table:columns.description: Source metadata dictionary indicating origin datasets and attribution.

table:columns.name: has_parts
table:columns.description: Indicates whether this building has related child components (e.g., annexes, wings).

table:columns.name: is_underground
table:columns.description: True if the building is fully or partially underground.

table:columns.name: class
table:columns.description: Building classification (e.g., residential, commercial, industrial) based on Overture schema.

table:columns.name: height
table:columns.description: Estimated building height in meters above ground level.

table:columns.name: num_floors
table:columns.description: Estimated number of floors above ground.

geoparquet-stac-items.title: GeoParquet STAC items
geoparquet-stac-items.description: Snapshot of the collection's STAC items exported to GeoParquet format.
